You sure you were looking at Horizons?  I've seen people say the graphics are worse than pre-kunark, and I've heard people say they're better than SW:G.  I play the game on Medium graphic settings, and I must say it's absolutely stunning.  When I set it to Highest for screenshots, it's even more stunning.  The graphics are pretty immersive for me, and the gameplay suits my fancy more so than EQ has in the last 6 years.<br>
