<br>
The armour in particular, doesn't look convincing at all and often appears to have been spray painted onto the characters rather than being something they are actually wearing. This is all assuming that you get to see the real character model at all instead of those awful grey placeholders the game displays until the character data has finished loading.<br>
<br>
I'm still enjoying the game but I can see how people might consider it to be both better and worse than EQ graphically.<br>
<br>
As an aside, the music is excellent. First online game where I haven't switched off the tunes after a few hours play <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
